ENGLISH
================================================================================

This source code is made publicly visible FOR REVIEW and for PERSONAL, LOCAL,
NON-COMMERCIAL USE ONLY. It is NOT open-source software and does not grant the
usual redistribution rights.

YOU MAY:
  - download/clone the code;
  - run it on your own machine for strictly personal use;
  - modify it locally, for yourself.

YOU MAY NOT, without the author's prior written permission:
  - redistribute, republish or host the code or any derivative (including on
    another repository, website, hosting or platform);
  - offer the software as a service to third parties (public/hosted/SaaS);
  - use the project, in whole or in part, for commercial purposes or to generate
    revenue (subscriptions, ads, sale, etc.);
  - remove this license or the copyright notices.

WHY THESE RESTRICTIONS:
  The app aggregates listings from third-party sites (e.g. OLX, Storia) whose
  Terms of Service forbid extracting, aggregating and commercially reusing their
  data. Therefore local, personal use (each person for themselves) is private use
  and far more defensible, whereas publishing a public service or making money
  from their data would breach those sites' terms and database-rights law. Hence
  public distribution and commercial use are not permitted.

WARRANTY:
  The software is provided "AS IS", without any warranty. The author is not
  liable for any damages. If you run the app, you are solely responsible for
  complying with each source site's Terms of Service and applicable law.

For any other use (commercial, redistribution, partnership) contact the author:
cezartocaciu233@gmail.com.
